import axios from 'axios' import React, { useRef, useState } from 'react' const Full_stack_crud = () => { const first_name = useRef() const last_name = useRef() const email = useRef() const password = useRef() const confirm_password = useRef() const [input, setinput] = useState({}) const submit_handler = () => { const input = { first_name: first_name.current.value, last_name: last_name.current.value, email: email.current.value, password: password.current.value, confirm_password: confirm_password.current.value, } setinput(input) } const API_handler = () => { axios.post("http://192.168.235.252:5500/v1/user/create").then((res) => console.log(res)).catch((err) => console.log(err)) } return ( <>
) } export default Full_stack_crud
